Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0250,,#23 停轉世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:48.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無盡的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爺可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM系統
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托付…給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰哥 米迦哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.20,0:00:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這搭載在Gundam上的功能是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veda數據中沒有相關資料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.66,0:00:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是預先載入GN Drive的黑匣子裏的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 Veda中Meister們的數據似乎被徹底刪除了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·舒恩伯格連我變更計劃都預測到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以神自居的理想主義者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要耍弄我們到何時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.45,0:01:17.68,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}拉格朗日1 資源衛星群
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強襲用集裝箱 開始連接到托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾部推進器 收納完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在敵人打過來之前完成整備 趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將機體中積蓄的高濃度壓縮粒子全面釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.27,0:01:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一定時間內獲得將性能提高三倍的功率
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有原型太陽爐才有的機能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM系統
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞老爹還給我們留下這麼好的禮物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:02:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 使用TRANS-AM之後 機體性能會急劇下降
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所謂雙刃劍…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那發來的密信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 收到返回托勒密的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有要件報告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面上的擬造太陽爐搭載型MS 全部上了宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.86,0:02:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 一架Gundam Throne被敵方俘獲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俘獲？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是聯合國軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪取Throne的機師 是阿利·阿爾·薩謝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿利·阿爾·薩謝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那混蛋要來這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把人耍到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是傭兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是補給先結束 還是聯合國軍先來犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 都得在拉格朗日1打一仗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:52.93,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}聯合國軍 維吉尼亞級大型運輸艦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:03:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然專門準備了備用零件 夠省心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你俘獲這架Gundam的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是頂武特種部隊的瑟爾蓋·史米盧佐夫中校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙俄羅斯的荒熊親自來打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是法國第4獨立外籍騎兵聯隊的蓋利·比亞吉少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特來參加Gundam討伐作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挺想聽聽看 你是如何俘獲Gundam的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是商業機密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離可視戰鬥宙域 還有2000
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員 第一戰鬥配置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS部隊準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一刻終於來了 哈瓦德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複 離可視戰鬥宙域…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到答案了嗎 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我們 收到了伊奧利亞·舒恩伯格的托付
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:04:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我會以自己的意志 為根除戰爭而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與Gundam一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 我可沒覺得我們能夠做到根除戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我們這些愚蠢的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論好壞 都會銘刻在人們心中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我才開始思考 「天人」…我們 到底有什麼存在的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類只對自己親身經歷過的事物 才能從真正意義上理解它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 捕捉到聯合國軍的艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近中的敵方運輸艦 推測為UNION的維吉尼亞級 數量三架
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離可視戰鬥區域 還有4200
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用資源衛星 托勒密後退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios Virtue 準備防衛戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 在托勒密內待機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 別這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做是不是強硬了點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用說的他可不會聽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在上次戰鬥中被他所救
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 這次就由我來保護他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 固定到電磁領域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 阿勒路亞·哈普提森 開始迎擊行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方運輸艦中有MS出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue 提耶利亞·艾迪 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:06:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方MS為擬GN Drive搭載型 26架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方MS部隊中發現Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告所有機師 出擊的Gundam只有兩架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用245陣型應戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用包圍戰殲滅之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校 請期待我的戰果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~ 哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位真起勁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先發制人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新裝備嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用尾部推進器提高機動性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機 陣型別打亂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按E計劃各個擊破
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊無效
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ Throne嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉它 Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面請自便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗體E57
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索瑪·比利斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 尾部推進器破損
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和疑似超兵的MS交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue 正遭到敵方MS的集中性攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對Gundam下達撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.14,0:08:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦橋 能聽見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用GN-Armer進行對艦攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按你的戰術辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉要你陪我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿利·阿爾·薩謝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完了 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭…頭疼消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦量子波被我屏蔽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了他們 阿勒路亞
